-According to collected research statistics the Ukrainian women are underrepresented in Ukrainian political life. This is a very important issue because the extent of women’s involvement in politics and their access to decision-making is a key indicator of gender equality in a society.{{sfn|Ukrainian Women’s Fund|2011|p=4|loc=Current Situation Analysis}}
